title: Here Comes the Godly Emperor: I Have Billions of Attribute Points
description: With trillions of attribute points and endless magic treasures,Yi Qingtian was reincarnated on earth, only to encounter divine punishment at his birth. To save the lives of his family, he transforms and violently beats the Heavenly Dao, only to have nine seals of destruction casted upon him conversely. To break them, he must find the nine heavenly books and the nine scholars. Thus, he embarks on a journey to defy the Heavenly Dao.
